how to get inside the castle.

1193
01:43:09.350 --> 01:43:12.394
- [Thunder Rumbles]
- Ocht veth bordak stira.

1194
01:43:12.478 --> 01:43:16.940
Ocht veth bordak stira.
Ocht veth bordak stira.

1195
01:43:17.066 --> 01:43:20.443
Ocht veth bordak stira.
[Thunder Rumbles]

1196
01:43:20.528 --> 01:43:23.363
Ocht veth bordak stira.

1197
