will never work.

1199
01:43:28.119 --> 01:43:31.329
If the baby dies.
all hope for the future is lost.

1200
01:43:33.040 --> 01:43:35.625
I'm going to fight.

1201
01:43:38.963 --> 01:43:40.964
Me too.

1202
01:43:47.680 --> 01:43:51.266
