who's gonna go and who's gonna stay.

1203
01:44:34.477 --> 01:44:36.686
[Chattering]

1204
01:44:38.856 --> 01:44:41.191
Raziel.

1205
01:44:41.275 --> 01:44:46.196
Willow. all these years
I have waited to face Bavmorda.

1206
01:44:46.280 --> 01:44:49.532
